Regression¶

Regresi adalah sebuah algoritma atau konsep yang bekerja dengan melakukan pemodelan terhadap hubungan antara variabel-variable yang diperbaharui (refined) secara iterasi dengan menggunakan pengukuran error pada hasil prediksi yang dihasilkan oleh model. Regresi paling dikenal dengan linear dan logistik regresi dengan melakukan pemodelan hubungan antara variabel dependen (y) dengan variabel-variabel independen diketahui sebagai (x)

Buat label encode dan dummy encode pada fitur kategorikal¶

In [16]:
df=df.reset_index(drop=True)
le=LabelEncoder()  #untuk encode fitur kategorikal yang lain
oe=OneHotEncoder() #untuk membuat dummy-encode dari fitur furnished

col=[col for col in df.select_dtypes(include='O').columns if col != 'furnishingstatus']

#label encode fitur kategorical
df[col]=df[col].apply(le.fit_transform)

#one-hot encode fitur kategorikal lain
oe_df=pd.DataFrame(oe.fit_transform(df[['furnishingstatus']]).toarray(),
                  columns=oe.get_feature_names())
df=df.drop(['furnishingstatus'], axis=1)
df=df.join(oe_df)

#data for linear regression
x_lin=df.drop(['price'], axis=1)
y_lin=df['price']
y_lin=np.reshape(y_lin.values,(-1,1))

#data for classification
x_log=df.drop(['mainroad'], axis=1)
y_log=df['mainroad']

x_train_lin, x_test_lin, y_train_lin, y_test_lin=train_test_split(x_lin,y_lin, test_size=0.3, random_state=42)
x_train_log, x_test_log, y_train_log, y_test_log=train_test_split(x_log,y_log, test_size=0.3, random_state=42)

Melakukan Standardized atau Normalisasi terhadap Data¶

In [19]:
scaled_columns_lin=['area','bedrooms','bathrooms','stories','parking']
scaled_columns_log=['price','area','bedrooms','bathrooms','stories','parking']

#Scaler
mm=MinMaxScaler() #for linear regression

sc=StandardScaler() #for logistic regression/classification

#Scaling Data For Linear Regression

x_train_lin[scaled_columns_lin]=mm.fit_transform(x_train_lin[scaled_columns_lin])
x_test_lin[scaled_columns_lin]=mm.transform(x_test_lin[scaled_columns_lin])
y_train_lin=mm.fit_transform(y_train_lin)
y_test_lin=mm.transform(y_test_lin)

#Scaling Data For logistic Regression

x_train_log[scaled_columns_log]=sc.fit_transform(x_train_log[scaled_columns_log])
x_test_log[scaled_columns_log]=sc.transform(x_test_log[scaled_columns_log])

Gunakan Grid Search pada Linear dan Logistic Regression¶

In [26]:
from sklearn.model_selection import KFold, StratifiedKFold, GridSearchCV

#Linear Regression
lin_r=LinearRegression()
lin_r.fit(x_train_lin,y_train_lin)

#Logistic Regression
log_r=LogisticRegression()
log_r.fit(x_train_log, y_train_log)

#Recursive Feature Elimination
#linear
rfe_lin=RFE(lin_r)

#Logistic
rfe_log=RFE(log_r)

#create cross validation
folds=KFold(n_splits=10, shuffle=True, random_state=42)
sfolds=StratifiedKFold(n_splits=10, shuffle=False, random_state=None)

#tentukan parameter yang ingin dioptimalkan
hyper_params=[{'n_features_to_select': list(range(1,16))}]

#develop model with GridSearch for linear regression
model_linear=GridSearchCV(estimator=rfe_lin,
                       param_grid=hyper_params,
                       scoring='neg_mean_squared_error',
                       cv=folds,
                       verbose=1,
                       return_train_score=True)

model_logistic=GridSearchCV(estimator=rfe_log,
                       param_grid=hyper_params,
                       scoring='accuracy',
                       cv=sfolds,
                       verbose=1,
                       return_train_score=True)

model_linear.fit(x_train_lin, y_train_lin)
model_logistic.fit(x_train_log, y_train_log)

linear_report=pd.DataFrame(model_linear.cv_results_)
logistic_report=pd.DataFrame(model_logistic.cv_results_)

#Best parameter and score
print('best parameter for linear regression', model_linear.best_params_)
print('best score for linear regression', model_linear.best_score_)

print('best parameter for logistic regression', model_logistic.best_params_)
print('best score for logistic regression', model_logistic.best_score_)

from sklearn.model_selection import cross_validate

#Calling regression model
lin_r=LinearRegression()
log_r=LogisticRegression()

#Using Recursive Feature Elimination
rfe_lin=RFE(estimator=lin_r, n_features_to_select=12)
rfe_log=RFE(estimator=log_r, n_features_to_select=13)

scoring_lin=['r2','neg_mean_squared_error','neg_mean_absolute_error']
scoring_log=['accuracy','precision','recall','f1','average_precision','roc_auc']

#Cross Validation for linear regression
cv_lin=cross_validate(estimator=rfe_lin, X=x_train_lin, 
                      y=y_train_lin, cv=10, 
                      scoring=scoring_lin)

#Cross Validation for logistic regression
cv_log=cross_validate(estimator=rfe_log, X=x_train_log, 
                      y=y_train_log, cv=10, 
                      scoring=scoring_log)

cv_lin_score=pd.DataFrame(cv_lin)
cv_lin_score.index+=1

cv_log_score=pd.DataFrame(cv_log)
cv_log_score.index+=1
